  "time_ut": 1660788228,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0d87\u0dc5\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0d9c\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0db8\u0dba\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9 \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The villager who threw a child into the canal is guilty of work",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that the Udapola village officer was arrested in connection with an incident in which an 8-year-old child was picked up and thrown into the canal and injured while watching an elephant bathe in a canal in the Polgahawela Udapola area.",
        "The police also mention that the child was taken to the hospital with a broken bone as a result of the suspect's actions.",
        "The police also mention that while this child was watching the elephant bathing from the bank of the canal, the suspect who was passing by the place picked up the child and threw him to the place where the elephant was.",
        "According to the complaint made by the child's parents to the police regarding the incident, the police have arrested the suspect.",
        "The police say that the suspect is a (54)-year-old man and that he was drunk."
      ],
